item.title: Code of Conduct
item.description: Code of Conduct GDG Vizag / Community Group is dedicated to providing a harassment-free and inclusive event experience for everyone regardless of gender identity and expression, sexual orientation, disabilities, neurodiversity, physical appearance, body size, ethnicity, nationality, race, age, religion, or other protected category. We do not tolerate harassment of event participants in any form. GDG Vizag / Community Group takes violations of our policy seriously and will respond appropriately.
